Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.42,0:00:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, sign this document.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can be the happiest kid in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"With no year limit and no payment, it will be possessed as an asset..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good kid, good... Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobio!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot Circus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the gift from this trip. His name is Tobio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get to work right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, it's a small robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I'm sure we can use him for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassy, you take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm busy. I have to practice tightrope-act and ring-of-fire act.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have to take care of robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Teaching this one is going to be a hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you talk back to Tornedo! You are only a newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the best one in this group!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tornedo's turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a robot, too, right? Does he get beaten as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We hired an inventor to make Tornedo with a high expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a specially-made robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's way above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, you will see once you take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, a midair play with thrill, speed and suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After passing through a 50,000 volt current,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,will he be able to reach that golden end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know? Around that ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a high-voltage current is flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the one who can calculate the time precisely
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,can catch that end of the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor robot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that's only a fake act.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've waited long enough! The next one is our biggest celebrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tornedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at his chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's most precise clock, the one that can measure 1/10000 second,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"The micro-second meter" is installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see? Now that you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you dare disobey the orders of Tornedo and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, newbie, are you working hard enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not putting much effort. Make it more shiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassy, the newbie must be doing all right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cleaning the white lion over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A white lion? Is there such thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this white one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cleaning the black-striped dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! It's tiger's stripe! You are fired! Fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, it increased!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a useless... Ha ha ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't tear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You always fail because of too much strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and load it in conveyor. We will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hold on, hold on. What is this with a skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You always have your own way. Dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this will do. Hey, load it in conveyor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey! Stupid! You stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Load the robot! You stupid newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He caused trouble again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who breaks this important robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday you broke a motorcycle, and a trampoline the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How many more thing do you have to break?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! I'm going to discipline him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying his best. He breaks stuff because he works too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If he continues to do this... I'm going to be broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have brought this useless stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make an orangutan or something after disassembling this! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait for only three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach him for sure in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang! Fine, I'll give you three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail to do so, he's going to become an orangutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That clown is still a kid robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing. In the near future,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the Declaration of Robot Rights is going to be valid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A place like this is old-fashioned as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the same for Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of this, what happened to that infamous son robot of Doctor Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... A good output, a good electronic brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that it's a high-performance robot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that no one's ever been able to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, it's already time for the meeting. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The news from Japan is being broadcasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After Doctor Tenma has gone missing, The Minister of Science...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu! You are going to be appointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have been deeply in thought since a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That robot looks exactly like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,With Tobio. Doctor Tenma's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tornedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing! The audience is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I'm in a bad condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't received Overhole for 5 months already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on until this tour finishes. Besides, in tonight's performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there's Mr. Capone from Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, you have waited long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest celebrity of this robot circus, Mr. Tornedo is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That clown received a fairly good response from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Cassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken! 1/550 second late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You shouldn't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, Mr. Tornedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tornedo... You are in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mr. Capone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was embarrassing, Hamegg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, it's not all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but if I noticed only a second earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have helped Tornedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to cancel the contract of the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we have to pay penalty fees?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the 50,000-voltage act,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamegg's circus has no merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Th..Then... I'm broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Capone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is an actor who can perform the voltage act,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to accept our team?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, but do you have such robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This little one? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible if he practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, but it could gain more popularity if a small robot like this performs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But this kind of newbie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him do it, Hamegg! I'll teach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, anyhow, I got him for free. He's a little one and he's broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it, Chief? Why don't we make him do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If the voltage act is back, then the contract is still in the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,After the tour in Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let go of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, fine, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Mr. Capone. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's troubling my heart a bit. It's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, please put Japan's Ministry of Science on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, the Ministry of Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you give me a data on Doctor Tenma's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The one on Tobio who died on a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobio Tenma, 9 years old at the point of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Height: 135cm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the circus team go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The train runs for Chicago, Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot Circus train runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Life in Circus team is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot Circus, tan tan tan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, tan tan tan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look where you are flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys... Are you trying to get me killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, please don't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just be crushed or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but if this Chicago tour fails, I will be broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to be able to do it by the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Chief, go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail this time, you are going to be an orangutan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Cassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still have some practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have some interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good feeling. Back in long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I received such attention from someone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but it feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a nice person had always been next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were a normal child,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say that they were my parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are no such things for robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I always cause trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to Cassy because of my mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are different. I'm not sure what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have big strength and wisdom that other robots don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Be confident. You will be able to do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We came a long way for Chicago, Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot Circus is going to be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, check this one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot Circus, tan tan tan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tan tan tan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals all seem out of heart today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the chief didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,give us enough injection of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Ever since Tornedo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,broke down, I'm all broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't move, maximize your output!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do such thing, it will break us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with talking back! You only have to endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, he's already energized!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassy, I don't know, you seem nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'll give you a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the shoes I wore on my first performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Do they fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They fit perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks quite good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the next stage is the famous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,50,000-voltage current act!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see a robot called Tobio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What business do you have with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Japanese scientist Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to protect that kid according to the International Robot Laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You have to stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a treasure I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Stop it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What am I going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a show like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the masterpiece of Doctor Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Mighty Robot" we've been dreaming of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, all components of this kid are all Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid and I have a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! You promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you would let him go if he succeeds with this act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never trust a verbal promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are sly. You are a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking and wash him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to ignore the Declaration of Robot Rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can lock him under such paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you must go back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the only one who can make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassy, what's up? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Oh, this would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the true value of that robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He can fly in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and under deep oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Now that I've heard that, I can't let him go even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh..What an evil man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are worse than a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... The gas container suddenly exploded...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, is this the best robot in Japan like you told me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Oh! You are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first got the call, I thought I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was surprised at those pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were all broken for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked hard to find things that would look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, we cannot let others see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget you, the small one yet with powerful strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, since this guy is an atomic boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Atomic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we call this kid "Atom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Fine! Good! It's a good name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Cassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We can meet again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked you, Atom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Atom. After coming back to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to go to elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher is the bearded man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I made many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, silly Shibugaki boys
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,went to a theme park that hasn't finished its construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Big trouble! My friends are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly over the sky with a jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A machine gun's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:24:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
